  "excerpt": "If the car in front of you is driving well below the speed limit,  why not  not tailgate him?",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "1 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If the car in front of you is driving well below the speed limit, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "why not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " not tailgate him?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If everyone is shouting at you (your boss, your kids, your clients), ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "why not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " respond calmly?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And if it seems like everyone in your industry is trying to ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "steal",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " attention (rather than earn it), ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "why not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " consider adopting a different strategy?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "/if-ogilvy-shrugged/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It doesn’t cost you any more to change your posture (or point of view), so why not try it and see what happens? ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Why not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " try the opposite?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Running towards a gorilla that’s escaped from the zoo (as opposed to evading it) isn’t a helpful way to be a contrarian. That’s not what I’m talking about. But finding an alternative exit (as opposed to be trampled by the mob of escapes) might be.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "My point is, doing the unpopular thing (and being smart about it) often has its benefits.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In situations where it doesn’t serve you to reciprocate in kind, to adopt the posture of tit-for-tat, or to follow the crowd—or the habitual thing—it helps tremendously to at least acknowledge you have a choice about how you respond, and what you choose to initiate.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
